-----BEGIN PGP SIGNED MESSAGE-----

Minor completion bug: have a buffer consisting of "''a", with the cursor
on the second "'", and press <tab>.  You get the "BUG: 0 <= wb <= cs <=
we is not true" message.

 -zefram

